messages.text: If the Init function took the enabled boolean, then we could pass it into the Delegate ctor, and get rid of the hardcoded true there for the initial state, I think?

messages.author: benm
messages.text:
I think this check only makes sense for the case that we're setting a new WebContents, so maybe move it up there?

So in SetWebContents we'd have:

if (save_form_data_ && !AutofillManager::FromWebContents(web_contents))
  InitAutofill()

wdyt?
